{
  "stem": "19982.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And thank God, I must say, if I look at my family, that Hitler didn't win.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[SOBBING] We won.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All time during the war they keep me-- only one thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would give up a long time-- just the thought that I would come back home, that I would come back to my parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only this thought kept me, because the life of a child alone, it's not life, especially between strangers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then-- but that kept me alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That kept me on the-- every single day, it's closer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's closer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will come home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's probably-- which I suffered so terribly then the disappointment that nobody's [SOBBING] alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had so many cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had so many aunts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were close with my cousins, and-- because the same town cousins-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody perished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a few times difficult times here also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Which I start to think-- and especially when I start to think, I had difficult times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had to go for help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- but now, the last doctor which I went was-- told me to write.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I write a lot now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this helps me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This helps me just to write my thoughts, my feelings, how I felt, and how-- and this helped me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so thank God I'm OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I'm strong enough to do-- if I look at my wonderful family, I have a wonderful husband, which I could say adores me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we are, thank God, financially comfortable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And wonderful children-- I have son in-laws, which are not sons-- which are not son-in-laws.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They are more than sons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They are really more than sons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SOBBING] So thank God for this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
